&lt;p id="AP5ub9"&gt;The plan also includes affordable EVs like its &lt;a href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/6/27/24187409/hyundai-inster-small-ev-compact-price-specs-us"&gt;Inster / Casper subcompact&lt;/a&gt;, the &lt;a href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/28/24230636/hyundai-ioniq-9-three-row-suv-us-extended-range"&gt;three-row Ioniq 9 that’s next up to launch in the US&lt;/a&gt;, luxury EVs from Genesis, and, finally, high-performance models. &lt;/p&gt;
