  &lt;p id="i3WCiX"&gt;After initially selling out, Sony’s &lt;a href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/29/24208726/astro-bot-limited-edition-ps5-dual-sense-controller"&gt;limited-edition&lt;em&gt; Astro Bot&lt;/em&gt; DualSense controller&lt;/a&gt; for the PS5 is available for preorder once again for $79.99. The forthcoming gamepad, which initially sold out but is now available from &lt;a href="https://goto.walmart.com/c/482924/565706/9383?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.walmart.com%2Fip%2FSony-PS5-DualSense-Wireless-Controller-Midnight-Black%2F9173864949%2F&amp;amp;sharedid=theverge.com" rel="sponsored nofollow noopener" target="_blank"&gt;Walmart&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href="https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.antonline.com%2FSony%2FAccessories%2FGaming_Accessories%2FGaming_Controllers%2F1510983%2F&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F24215774%2Fastro-bot-limited-edition-dualsense-wireless-controller-preorder-price-release-date-ps5" rel="sponsored nofollow noopener" target="_blank"&gt;Antonline&lt;/a&gt;, will launch alongside the &lt;a href="https://www.theverge.com/24167370/astro-bot-ps5-sequel-trailer-date"&gt;next &lt;em&gt;Astro Bot&lt;/em&gt; game&lt;/a&gt; on September 6th, giving those who’ve secretly been wishing their peripherals had more, huh, eyes, another option to consider.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="c-float-left c-float-hang"&gt;&lt;aside id="Ns5kju"&gt;&lt;div data-anthem-component="readmore" data-anthem-component-data='{"stories":[{"title":"4 great games I played at Summer Game Fest 2024","url":"https://www.theverge.com/2024/6/19/24180304/summer-game-fest-2024-best-games"},{"title":"Is this the PS5 Pro?","url":"https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/29/24231231/is-this-the-ps5-pro"},{"title":"Sony’s PlayStation PC push now includes a controller customization app","url":"https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/27/24229509/sony-playstation-dualsense-edge-controller-app-pc"}]}'&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/aside&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p id="mFjU3J"&gt;This isn’t the first time Sony Interactive Entertainment has released a special-edition controller to commemorate an upcoming exclusive — it launched a symbiote-themed controller alongside &lt;a href="https://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/marvels-spider-man-2/limited-editions/?"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Marvel’s Spider-Man 2&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt; last year — but its latest collaboration with developer Team Asobi is far cuter. The new PS5 controller features shiny...&lt;/p&gt;
